subproject.description: This is a 5 year, Multi-donor program managed by UNDP, in support of 7 democratic institutions ( Eth Human Rights Commission, Eth Institute of the Ombudsman, National Election Board, Federal and regional Parilaments, House of Federation, Federal Ethics and Anticorruption Commission and the federal and regional audit offices). The project aims at building the institutional capacity of these new institutions  to help them carry out thier missions effectively
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Democratic Institution Program
